title: 'DO READ BEFORE BUYING!!!'
body: So 3M is a very reputed brand and thinking the same thing I went for this product. The packaging was great and had 2 complete rolls.  The quality of the tape itself is awesome, the adhesive is great, the quality of the tape itself is good.  The only issue is, the tape seems to be precut, both the rolls. I mean you can see on the 3rd image that there is a line that goes till the center so you wont be able to control the length of the tape that you need if you purchase this. It wasn't an issue with me but might be for you so do remember that. The length of the tape that you can get on every pull is 20cm.

title: 'Thin but doesn’t tear or break easily'
